festival.introText: Since starting in 2006 their all-day festival has grown into a rite of passage for lovers of pop-punk and rock music alike. With 8 stages of bands and thousands of like-minded festival goers Slam Dunk Festival is now a key date in the summer festival calendar.

faqs.question: When is Slam Dunk Festival - North 2023?
faqs.answer: Slam Dunk Festival - North takes place on Sunday 28th May 2023.

faqs.question: How do I get to Slam Dunk Festival - North?
faqs.answer:
Slam Dunk Festival - North is accessible from Leeds City Train Station by either shuttle bus or taxi.

The festival is running a shuttle bus from Leeds City Centre directly to the festival site and back again.

 

For more info on other travel options, please visit https://www.slamdunkfestival.com/travel-north-info

faqs.question: What happens if I bought a ticket and cannot attend?
faqs.answer: Unfortunately we can’t issue you with a refund if you can’t make the event due to work commitments or your mates have dropped out. In these circumstances, we advise passing on your tickets privately to avoid losing out on the money spent. Refunds can only be offered if the event is cancelled or postponed, as agreed upon purchase.

faqs.question: Does Slam Dunk Festival - North have onsite camping?
faqs.answer: No, Slam Dunk Festival - North is a non-camping festival so camping equipment is not needed.

faqs.question: Accessibility information
faqs.answer: For full access information (including info on companion tickets, viewing platforms, and accessible facilities) please visit https://www.slamdunkfestival.com/access

faqs.question: Where is Slam Dunk Festival - North?
faqs.answer: Slam Dunk Festival - North takes place at Temple Newsam in Leeds; a 15-20 minute drive from the city centre.

faqs.question: Does Slam Dunk Festival - North have any age restrictions?
faqs.answer:
Slam Dunk Festival - North is an all-ages event. Under 5s go free but will need a ticket.

 

Afterparties (11pm onwards) are STRICTLY 18+ and you may be asked to provide photo ID.

faqs.question: When does Slam Dunk Festival - North start?
faqs.answer:
The gates for Slam Dunk Festival - North will open at 9am with the main arena opening at 11am.

 

Afterparties run from 11pm - 4am.
